All five phases are **PASS**; `validate_mcp_v2_gates.sh --all` exits 0.

To run embedding recall audit locally after caching the model:

```bash
pip install -e '.[embeddings]'
# download all-MiniLM-L6-v2 once (offline thereafter)
context-eng-ml-eval
```
